{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-ST-2", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "啟程", "storyInfo": "夢境已經結束，眾人前進的道路卻尚未終結。萬眾矚目的時刻即將來臨。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g1_outdoorbase", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西......多蘿西！你沒事吧？！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 9, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很好。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢、慢一點，你就快撞上我了......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都怪我，要是我早點發現斐爾迪南有問題，要是我能早點想辦法提醒大家，要是我能多陪你聊一聊，要是......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你呀......從監控站一路趕過來，臉頰都沾上灰了。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也可能是揍斐爾迪南的時候沾上的。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我都忘了當時隨手拿起來的是什麼東西......我的手抖得很厲害。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你出氣了嗎？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，我一點都不覺得爽快。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西，我很失望，然後是憤怒，而當事情塵埃落定，我看著士兵們追著他衝出去......我又很難過。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為斐爾迪南做的這些事？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，因為他......他本可以做到的事。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是我說，直到此刻，我都依然記得他教我的每一件事，依然相信訴說那些宏大的理想時，他眼裡的光不完全是假的......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以及......我曾經最想要的......不過是他的認可......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我是不是特別傻？", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這毫無問題，埃琳娜。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有時候......接受會比否定更難。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你以後不再是任何人的助手。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你身上不會有他的影子，可你的眼睛裡留下了他燃過的火，你的起點正是他的終點，你無疑會走得比他更遠。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多蘿西......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說這些話，怎麼聽起來像告別？什麼叫我不再是任何人的助手......我知道你把自己接入“中樞”了，你的身體該不會出問題了吧？！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......別著急。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我真的沒事，不信的話，你可以問問我們的好醫生......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我什麼都保證不了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利維亞，拓荒者們的身體檢查都結束了？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡還有最後一位。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“遞質”仍在你們體內流動。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "目前你們的身體沒有表現出任何異樣，可未來的情況如何，誰都無法下判斷。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必為我擔心，親愛的醫生。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些流淌在我體內的物質，不會比生長在你們身上的結晶......和前方隨時會降臨的風暴更有威脅。", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我們都不會因此停下，不是嗎？", "name": "多蘿西"}, "figure_art": "avg_4048_doroth_1#8$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "失控的造物對基地的破壞很徹底。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前並沒有多少廢墟，只有滿地銀白留了下來。"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不了多久，就連它們都會被清理乾淨。"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是痕跡......痕跡終究存在。"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前的銀色河流突然再次動了起來。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是雨雲的倒影啊......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#7$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g7_mainstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......消息已收到。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "基地的事情已由政府接手。按照約定，羅德島需要將得到的情報銷毀。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但事情並不會就此結束。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛得到了一條新的線索，關於斐爾迪南背後的支持者，我目前正在去見線人的路上。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士......", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#9$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "29_i09", "xScale": 0.85, "yScale": 0.85, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "duration": 40.0, "xScaleFrom": 0.85, "xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleFrom": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭停下了腳步，抬起頭。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雨雲正從城外的方向慢慢地飄過來。"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一百多公里之外的基地裡......"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一個人的腦子裡也冒出了相同的念頭。"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特里蒙就快下雨了。", "name": "赫默&塞雷婭"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g1_outdoorbase", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......到這裡就可以了。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝你幫我們收拾東西，格雷伊。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很高興自己能幫上一點忙，桑尼先生。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且能收拾的東西......呃，不太多。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "挺好，和來的時候差不多。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請務必向你的同事們傳達我們的歉意與感謝。羅德島的諸位的確就跟你說的一樣，將我們從絕望的境地中拉了出來。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是的，桑尼先生，是您和其餘拓荒者救了自己。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您忘了嗎？要不是您發出了“聲音”，我們並沒有機會抓住您的手。", "name": "格雷伊"}, "figure_art": "avg_1027_greyy2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "擁有像你這樣的朋友真是一樁幸事。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "工程師先生，我會記住你說的話，還有基地裡發生的一切。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有瑪麗......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確保你們全部離開基地是我的工作。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想說，你還有機會......逮捕我的機會。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#3$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次事件只是一場由個人違規行為引起的實驗事故——這是上頭給的說法。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然那幾位萊茵的研究員也不準備再追究下去，你的“綁架”行為也不會被記錄在案。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我不是說這兩天的事。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是......四年前。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我那一天晚上為什麼想去報名參加實驗嗎？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每個拓荒者都有想回到城市裡的理由。而我的理由是......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要回去找那個被我深深傷害過的人——我曾經最親密的朋友。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我欠她一個道歉，以及——", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的所作所為理應被審判。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經逃了四年多。最初我以為是荒野吞噬了我的夢想，讓我變得越來越不像自己......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實並不是。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四年前的那一個夜晚，是我親手殺死了過去那個追求公平正義的桑尼·羅馬諾。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是被捕的話，你可能會面臨兩種懲罰。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一種是進監獄，刑滿之後進感染者收治區。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另一種......", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為一名拓荒者，移動城市的入口永遠對你封閉。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你已經是拓荒者了。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，你......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別再說什麼原諒不原諒的話了，老朋友來送你一程，不該抓緊時間做點更有意義的事嗎？", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個久違的，溫暖的擁抱。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是真正的重逢，也是時隔多年的正式告別。"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想好之後去哪裡了嗎？", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#3$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個名字是D開頭的一連串字母的人，前幾天給我們發了一封有些古怪的郵件，附上了一則工作邀請。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還沒弄明白他是怎麼拿到我們拓荒隊的聯繫方式的......他一點都不像仲介公司的人。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......下次接工作記得謹慎些。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#3$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_527_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也別再嘗試犯罪。否則的話，不管你跑多遠，我都會把你揪回來。我保證。", "name": "瑪麗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_527_1#2$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#2$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，警長。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#3$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拓荒隊的兄弟姐妹們正在不遠處呼喊他的名字。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼知道，這一次，自己真正做好了啟程的準備。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g2_edgeofbase", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attr